      "title": "Businessman\u2019s son abducted from Wattala",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "COLOMBO (News 1st); An unidentifed group had abducted a young man from Kerawalapitiya, Wattala on Saturday (27) morning.",
        "It is reported that the sone of a wealthy businessman from Kandana was abducted at 11:15 AM on Saturday.",
        "The abduction victim was identified as Nadun Kaushalya Wijesinghe from Kandana.",
        "It was reported that the abductors had taken the young man away in his own White Range Rover SUV, and thereafter dumped the vehicles in Ekala."
      ],
